# Tables (GFM)

Basic:

| Name  | Role     |
| ----- | -------- |
| Alice | Author   |
| Bob   | Reviewer |

Alignment:

| Left | Center | Right |
| :--- | :----: | ----: |
| a    |    b   |     c |
| dd   |   ee   |    ff |

Compact:

| a | b | c |
| - | - | - |
| 1 | 2 | 3 |

With escapes and pipes:

| Symbol | Meaning      |
| ------ | ------------ |
| `\|`   | pipe literal |
| `\\`   | backslash    |
